@startuml
title Dynamic Production Routes

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor White
    BorderColor Black
    ArrowColor Black
}

partition "Product A" {
    start
    :Deploy from Source 1;
    :Request Crane;
    :Transport to Process 1;
    :Run Process 1;
    :Request Crane;
    :Transport to Sink;
    stop
}

partition "Product B" {
    start
    :Deploy from Source 2;
    :Request Crane;
    :Transport to Process 2;
    :Run Process 2;
    :Request Crane;
    :Transport to Process 1;
    :Run Process 1;
    :Request Crane;
    :Transport to Sink;
    stop
}

note right
The Part Agent determines the route.

The Crane Agent does not know:
- Product type
- Production plan
- Required process sequence

It only receives source and destination coordinates.
end note

@enduml